1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 17=

16
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,820
(Xu Zhaohe)
(Hello, Dr. Zhou?)

17
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:50,050
(May I know)

18
00:01:50,050 --> 00:01:51,100
(how's Yuci today?)

19
00:01:51,690 --> 00:01:52,980
(Dr. Zhou)
(Same as yesterday.)

20
00:01:53,050 --> 00:01:54,020
(Still in a coma.)

21
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:03,570
Mom,

22
00:02:03,570 --> 00:02:05,380
I want to go downstairs and play.

23
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:08,060
Mom, it's snowing.

24
00:02:08,130 --> 00:02:09,940
Take me sledding.

25
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:14,610
Mom,

26
00:02:14,850 --> 00:02:17,890
can you take me to see the sea again
during summer break?

27
00:02:26,980 --> 00:02:27,780
Mom,

28
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:29,340
I still want that cake

29
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:30,730
from Grandma's birthday.

30
00:02:30,780 --> 00:02:32,730
Can you buy me another one?

31
00:02:33,170 --> 00:02:34,290
Pretty please.

32
00:02:39,890 --> 00:02:40,690
Mom,

33
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:43,730
I was named Outstanding Student Leader
of the district today.

34
00:02:43,890 --> 00:02:45,100
The teacher praised me

35
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:46,010
at the school assembly.

36
00:02:46,010 --> 00:02:47,570
I was also chosen to raise the flag.

37
00:03:04,180 --> 00:03:07,900
(One month later)

38
00:03:35,850 --> 00:03:36,890
It's snowing.

39
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:55,340
Do you know this is a dream?

40
00:03:57,290 --> 00:03:58,220
I know.

41
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:02,410
Do you still hate me?

42
00:04:05,220 --> 00:04:06,940
Has your pain gone away?

43
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,010
It's strange though.

44
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:18,900
I don't feel any hatred

45
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:22,370
or pain.

46
00:04:24,490 --> 00:04:26,170
In real life,

47
00:04:26,580 --> 00:04:27,980
I hated you so much

48
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:30,930
and wanted to get back at you.

49
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:35,580
But when I actually

50
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:36,930
did those things,

51
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:40,850
I didn't feel happy at all.

52
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:45,730
I felt miserable.

53
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:04,700
Right now,

54
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,370
this feels the best.

55
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:11,170
It's so peaceful.

56
00:05:13,930 --> 00:05:14,850
I really wish

57
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:16,580
I could stay here forever.

58
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:20,490
Like nothing ever happened.

59
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,370
Like it's still

60
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,780
just you and me.

61
00:05:26,780 --> 00:05:28,580
The way things used to be.

62
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,020
That would be so nice.

63
00:05:39,810 --> 00:05:40,610
Yes.

64
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:45,540
Staying in a peaceful fantasy

65
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,460
does feel nice.

66
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,660
Has it ever occurred to you

67
00:06:13,610 --> 00:06:15,540
why things end up like this for you?

68
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:18,700
Why were you abandoned by everyone?

69
00:06:21,340 --> 00:06:22,660
Your dad despises you.

70
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,980
Your mom keeps you at arm's length.

71
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:28,100
The friends and lover you trusted

72
00:06:28,100 --> 00:06:29,730
joined forces to turn against you.

73
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,610
Have you ever thought about why?

74
00:06:42,050 --> 00:06:44,250
I'm not staying here with you.

75
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,140
Because I,

76
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:47,810
Bai Liangliang,

77
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:49,930
will not stop

78
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,980
for anyone or anything.

79
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:22,860
(Three years earlier)

80
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:27,820
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

81
00:07:34,730 --> 00:07:35,810
I'm sorry, Yuci.

82
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,700
For your safety,

83
00:07:37,850 --> 00:07:39,020
we have to do this.

84
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:45,610
Get some rest.

85
00:07:48,850 --> 00:07:49,980
Doctor, is there

86
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:51,250
any stronger medication

87
00:07:55,700 --> 00:07:57,610
that can make me forget everything

88
00:07:57,610 --> 00:07:59,020
in my head?

89
00:07:59,170 --> 00:08:00,540
Alright. Try not to think about it.

90
00:08:50,580 --> 00:08:51,940
Alright. Next.

91
00:08:58,340 --> 00:09:01,420
(Queue up for medication)

92
00:09:07,460 --> 00:09:08,700
Next, please.

93
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:35,490
Next.

94
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:37,700
Good. Next.

95
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,890
Very well. Next.

96
00:09:42,890 --> 00:09:47,620
(Queue up for medication. Month)

97
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:57,470
Hey, little girl. Don't cry.

98
00:11:01,890 --> 00:11:03,140
Who are you?

99
00:11:03,580 --> 00:11:06,530
I'm Mr. Rabbit.
I'm here to help you, Duoduo.

100
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:18,420
Thank you.

101
00:11:19,090 --> 00:11:21,440
Why are you helping me?

102
00:11:21,820 --> 00:11:23,020
Because I know

103
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:25,160
everyone feels scared and alone

104
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,990
in a strange place.

105
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:28,980
The reason I exist

106
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:31,350
is to help people like you.

107
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:41,100
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

108
00:11:45,490 --> 00:11:46,370
Director Han,

109
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:49,580
can I take a paper crane?

110
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:50,770
Of course.

111
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:59,610
After the last dosage increase,

112
00:11:59,980 --> 00:12:02,100
have you had any discomfort?

113
00:12:09,490 --> 00:12:11,730
Can I see my family?

114
00:12:13,650 --> 00:12:14,490
Last time,

115
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:16,490
(Treatment Room)

116
00:12:16,530 --> 00:12:18,730
we brought your mother in,

117
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:22,890
but your emotions

118
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:24,580
weren't stable.

119
00:12:27,730 --> 00:12:28,530
Well.

120
00:12:29,220 --> 00:12:30,730
This is a self-assessment form.

121
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:32,300
Evaluate your condition.

122
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:34,770
Rate yourself based on

123
00:12:34,850 --> 00:12:36,180
how you feel.

124
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:43,060
(Self-Assessment Form)

125
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:45,460
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

126
00:12:48,940 --> 00:12:50,610
You should go out and get some sunlight.

127
00:12:50,650 --> 00:12:51,700
Our garden

128
00:12:51,700 --> 00:12:52,770
is quite beautiful.

129
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:09,370
Director Wang, we've completed
the self-assessment form.

130
00:13:09,370 --> 00:13:11,180
We'll need to compile them
this afternoon.

131
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:21,890
Alright.

132
00:13:33,130 --> 00:13:34,060
No problem.

133
00:13:38,500 --> 00:13:41,580
(Duty Room)

134
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,780
(For outside calls,
dial the main line first.)

135
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:37,600
There's a patient in the duty room!

136
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:41,770
Santie, go!

137
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:43,490
Block the ball.

138
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,060
What are you doing? Move.

139
00:14:47,060 --> 00:14:47,850
Open the door.

140
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,700
Mom, pick up the phone.

141
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:52,370
Mom, answer it.

142
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:54,980
Open the door.

143
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:56,890
Open the door.

144
00:14:56,890 --> 00:14:57,940
Get the key.

145
00:15:03,771 --> 00:15:05,250
Yuci, open the door!

146
00:15:06,220 --> 00:15:07,010
Liangliang,

147
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,370
answer the phone for me.

148
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,100
Mom!

149
00:15:19,010 --> 00:15:19,820
Mom.

150
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:22,220
Mom, I'm Yuci.

151
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:23,730
You...

152
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:26,610
- Can you come see me alone?
- Yuci, open the door.

153
00:15:26,850 --> 00:15:28,770
I have so much to say to you.

154
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:30,730
Mom, please.

155
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:33,060
Mom, say something.

156
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,010
Liangliang.

157
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,100
Who was it?

158
00:15:46,890 --> 00:15:48,770
Nothing. Just a spam call.

159
00:15:49,850 --> 00:15:51,130
I blocked the number.

160
00:15:55,770 --> 00:15:57,250
Yuci, open the door!

161
00:15:58,100 --> 00:15:59,340
Rao Yuci, open the door!

162
00:16:00,220 --> 00:16:01,060
The key's here.

163
00:16:01,250 --> 00:16:02,700
How did she get in there?

164
00:16:13,250 --> 00:16:14,730
Yuci, calm down.

165
00:16:14,730 --> 00:16:16,130
You're bleeding, Yuci.

166
00:16:16,130 --> 00:16:17,250
Trust me.

167
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:20,010
Your family wouldn't want
to see you like this, right?

168
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:23,770
My family...

169
00:16:27,010 --> 00:16:29,580
Can I make one more call?

170
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:34,180
Can I?

171
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:38,250
Yes. Go ahead.

172
00:16:44,650 --> 00:16:45,460
Hello, Dad?

173
00:16:45,890 --> 00:16:46,850
I'm Yuci.

174
00:16:48,730 --> 00:16:49,530
I'm busy.

175
00:16:50,010 --> 00:16:51,990
Listen to the doctor
and focus on your treatment.

176
00:17:58,140 --> 00:17:58,900
Take her away.

177
00:18:10,570 --> 00:18:11,490
Liangliang,

178
00:18:11,810 --> 00:18:13,570
you should visit me more often.

179
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:16,250
It gets lonely here by myself.

180
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:37,540
(Visiting Room)

181
00:18:38,940 --> 00:18:39,730
Sorry,

182
00:18:39,810 --> 00:18:41,050
this is a necessary precaution.

183
00:18:41,130 --> 00:18:42,620
The orderlies and I are right outside.

184
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:44,660
Call us if you need anything.

185
00:18:45,620 --> 00:18:46,420
Thank you.

186
00:18:54,490 --> 00:18:56,330
Your mom asked me to bring this to you.

187
00:18:57,420 --> 00:18:58,860
Your favorite plant.

188
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:03,010
Must've been hard for you.

189
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:05,940
You went through so much
to make that call,

190
00:19:06,660 --> 00:19:08,330
only to have me answer it.

191
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:15,290
Once a person's fate changes,

192
00:19:17,220 --> 00:19:19,140
even fate itself stops helping you.

193
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:25,330
Can you tell me

194
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,420
what exactly I did

195
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:30,980
to make you hate me so much?

196
00:19:34,050 --> 00:19:36,220
Why does there have to be a reason

197
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:38,940
to hurt someone you hate?

198
00:19:39,660 --> 00:19:41,860
Some things just don't have one.

199
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:46,180
Don't worry.

200
00:19:46,250 --> 00:19:48,770
I'll arrange for you to see your mother.

201
00:19:49,250 --> 00:19:50,940
But I'm curious.

202
00:19:54,570 --> 00:19:56,290
How will you face her?

203
00:19:57,380 --> 00:19:58,330
Will you

204
00:19:58,330 --> 00:20:00,010
hurt her again?

205
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:02,460
Will the two of you

206
00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:04,290
end up hating each other even more?

207
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:16,330
There's no sign of life

208
00:20:16,330 --> 00:20:16,980
in her eyes.

209
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:18,010
Like she's already dead.

210
00:20:19,090 --> 00:20:21,770
She's like Duoduo from the fairy tale.

211
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:26,530
We have to help her.

212
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:35,620
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

213
00:21:10,330 --> 00:21:11,050
Yuci,

214
00:21:11,050 --> 00:21:12,620
you were hiding candy.

215
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,810
There's plenty in the hall.

216
00:21:15,810 --> 00:21:17,010
If you like it,

217
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:18,220
you don't have to hide it.

218
00:21:18,810 --> 00:21:20,530
Move these over here.

219
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:37,460
Hey, little girl. Don't cry.

220
00:21:37,570 --> 00:21:38,900
Who are you?

221
00:21:39,210 --> 00:21:42,190
I'm Mr. Rabbit.
I'm here to help you, Duoduo.

222
00:21:45,250 --> 00:21:48,530
Flowers, bloom.

223
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:52,140
Butterflies, fly.

224
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:55,490
Bees, gather honey.

225
00:21:55,860 --> 00:21:58,330
Butterflies, fly.

226
00:21:58,700 --> 00:22:01,940
Butterflies, fly.

227
00:22:02,250 --> 00:22:05,290
Bees, gather honey.

228
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:08,620
Butterflies, fly.

229
00:22:08,900 --> 00:22:11,530
Flowers, so beautiful.

230
00:22:11,570 --> 00:22:13,700
Fly away.

231
00:22:27,570 --> 00:22:28,420
Square.

232
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:32,140
X squared equals thirteen.

233
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,730
(Playground)

234
00:23:41,010 --> 00:23:42,330
Lucky ball.

235
00:23:46,570 --> 00:23:47,620
Where are my pills?

236
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:51,460
Your pills?

237
00:23:52,570 --> 00:23:54,010
We've tried them.

238
00:23:55,140 --> 00:23:56,180
They won't kill you,

239
00:23:56,660 --> 00:23:58,570
but they'll mess up your brain.

240
00:24:00,050 --> 00:24:00,860
Miss,

241
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:04,090
we're Mr. Rabbit.

242
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:05,980
We'll help Duoduo.

243
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:06,700
That's right.

244
00:24:09,660 --> 00:24:11,220
Right, let me introduce you.

245
00:24:11,940 --> 00:24:13,290
This is Professor Yang.

246
00:24:13,330 --> 00:24:15,530
He used to be an office director
at a big company.

247
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:17,700
I'll introduce him properly.

248
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:20,220
This old troublemaker,

249
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:22,290
we call him Master.

250
00:24:22,810 --> 00:24:24,140
Don't underestimate him.

251
00:24:24,810 --> 00:24:27,330
He's a big shot in finance.

252
00:24:27,530 --> 00:24:29,050
From Guangdong.

253
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:32,620
I can see right through you.

254
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,460
I can tell right away

255
00:24:34,810 --> 00:24:36,980
you need friends now.

256
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:39,570
Yes. We're friends.

257
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:43,980
And friends help each other, right?

258
00:24:43,980 --> 00:24:44,620
Right.

259
00:24:48,770 --> 00:24:49,570
Don't go.

260
00:24:50,090 --> 00:24:50,940
Don't go.

261
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:54,700
Don't go.

262
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:55,660
Don't go.

263
00:24:56,900 --> 00:24:58,460
Miss, we're not scammers.

264
00:24:58,460 --> 00:25:00,090
We're just a bunch of lunatics.

265
00:25:00,490 --> 00:25:01,290
How about this?

266
00:25:01,290 --> 00:25:02,420
Make a wish.

267
00:25:02,460 --> 00:25:03,700
Let's see if

268
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:04,620
we can make it happen.

269
00:25:10,380 --> 00:25:11,180
A laptop.

270
00:25:56,100 --> 00:25:57,660
(Miss, your gift. Check it.)

271
00:26:02,900 --> 00:26:06,180
(Card Number. Password)

272
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:12,580
(Available balance)

273
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,250
Boom!

274
00:26:21,860 --> 00:26:22,860
Why bomb?

275
00:26:23,050 --> 00:26:24,730
You're not happy. Then I don't boom.

276
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:26,420
What's your deal?

277
00:26:26,490 --> 00:26:27,620
Boom if you want.

278
00:26:27,620 --> 00:26:28,700
Don't boom when you don't.

279
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:29,700
You think I couldn't?

280
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:30,180
Huh?

281
00:26:30,180 --> 00:26:30,860
Wait...

282
00:26:31,490 --> 00:26:32,660
Who exactly are you people?

283
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:34,220
Why are you giving me money?

284
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:35,700
The money is his.

285
00:26:35,980 --> 00:26:38,220
This whole center belongs to him.

286
00:26:38,530 --> 00:26:39,490
If money's not spent,

287
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,250
it's just paper.

288
00:26:41,700 --> 00:26:44,900
Take the money as your chips
for the next round of your game.

289
00:26:47,700 --> 00:26:48,900
From her eyes,

290
00:26:49,730 --> 00:26:51,380
I can see her soul.

291
00:26:52,490 --> 00:26:55,180
Her soul needs our help.

292
00:26:55,730 --> 00:26:56,530
Really?

293
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:58,140
Don't forget.

294
00:26:58,420 --> 00:27:00,420
I'm a psychology expert.

295
00:27:01,770 --> 00:27:03,110
We're willing to help you.

296
00:27:03,120 --> 00:27:04,380
Let us help you.

297
00:27:08,250 --> 00:27:09,860
I don't need anyone's help.

298
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:11,490
Miss.

299
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,330
Your fate has changed.

300
00:27:15,250 --> 00:27:16,860
Can you really live with that?

301
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:38,220
Each of us here

302
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:40,860
has our own story.

303
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:44,900
We've all been through pain like yours.

304
00:27:45,900 --> 00:27:47,420
We understand how you feel.

305
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:50,090
Me, Santie, and Master.

306
00:27:51,140 --> 00:27:52,530
We all want to help you.

307
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:54,860
We hope you can return

308
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:56,490
to a place where the sun shines bright

309
00:27:57,010 --> 00:27:59,620
and find true happiness again.

310
00:28:01,010 --> 00:28:03,250
The wheel of fate has started turning,

311
00:28:03,330 --> 00:28:04,770
but it hasn't stopped yet.

312
00:28:05,770 --> 00:28:06,620
Rao Yuci,

313
00:28:07,570 --> 00:28:08,420
be brave

314
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:10,140
and stand back up again.

315
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:14,660
You have to!

316
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:27,380
(Lysen Group Successfully Acquired
Chuxia Business Investigation)

317
00:28:34,140 --> 00:28:34,940
Next,

318
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:37,140
let me introduce these young people.

319
00:28:38,570 --> 00:28:39,570
Lysen has just signed

320
00:28:39,620 --> 00:28:40,730
an acquisition deal

321
00:28:40,730 --> 00:28:42,420
with the company they founded.

322
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:45,460
In my life, Chuxia meant

323
00:28:46,140 --> 00:28:48,980
friendship and love.

324
00:28:49,770 --> 00:28:51,330
It was the happiest time of my life

325
00:28:51,810 --> 00:28:54,050
and the best time for all of us.

326
00:29:07,900 --> 00:29:09,660
The weather is nice today.

327
00:29:10,220 --> 00:29:12,090
Looks like you've figured things out.

328
00:29:19,770 --> 00:29:21,290
Before I tell my story,

329
00:29:21,980 --> 00:29:23,620
I want to hear yours.

330
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:27,660
I'll tell you in the future.

331
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:29,770
Miss,

332
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:31,980
the most important thing is this.

333
00:29:31,980 --> 00:29:34,010
You came from that world

334
00:29:34,290 --> 00:29:35,570
with something unresolved.

335
00:29:36,420 --> 00:29:38,570
Don't let that fire inside you die out.

336
00:29:40,220 --> 00:29:42,290
Plan your moves.
Who goes first, who comes next.

337
00:29:43,290 --> 00:29:44,490
Figure out your targets.

338
00:29:44,490 --> 00:29:45,900
What do they want?

339
00:29:47,190 --> 00:29:48,980
Only then can you strike
and take them down.

340
00:29:52,490 --> 00:29:53,290
Faster.

341
00:29:53,570 --> 00:29:54,660
Faster. Watch your arms.

342
00:29:54,730 --> 00:29:55,530
Breathe.

343
00:29:55,570 --> 00:29:56,380
This guy

344
00:29:56,380 --> 00:29:57,900
used to be a professional

345
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:58,730
basketball player.

346
00:29:58,810 --> 00:30:00,730
He played overseas.

347
00:30:02,050 --> 00:30:03,730
A month before going abroad,

348
00:30:03,730 --> 00:30:04,900
he tore his Achilles tendon.

349
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:06,170
So he had to drop out of the match.

350
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:08,250
That's when he fell into
severe depression.

351
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:09,810
Today's target is

352
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:11,250
824 steps.

353
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:15,050
Professor Yang is
a real deal psychology professor.

354
00:30:15,050 --> 00:30:15,940
Later, he went into business

355
00:30:15,940 --> 00:30:18,150
and joined a company with
over ten thousand employees.

356
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:20,290
But under tremendous pressure

357
00:30:20,290 --> 00:30:21,860
and after losing family members,

358
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:23,730
he developed severe bipolar disorder.

359
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:27,860
You see.

360
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:31,490
From a person's movements

361
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:32,980
and the way they talk,

362
00:30:34,090 --> 00:30:36,220
you can often tell

363
00:30:36,770 --> 00:30:38,330
what they've been through.

364
00:30:39,570 --> 00:30:42,330
Analyze Nurse Liu.

365
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,980
What kind of story does she have?

366
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:50,460
(Lysen's "Gambling" Incident)
Just memorizing data

367
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,330
is nowhere near enough.

368
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:53,980
(Lysen Group Sets up Family Fund Office)
Never forget.

369
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,860
(The Li Family Restaurant's Shares Ratio)
Data can lie.

370
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:58,290
You have to see
what the data is really saying.

371
00:30:59,380 --> 00:30:59,810
(Total funds raised)

372
00:30:59,810 --> 00:31:01,290
Five seconds left.

373
00:31:01,380 --> 00:31:03,420
Three, two, one.

374
00:31:04,250 --> 00:31:04,940
Stop.

375
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:07,180
Reset.

376
00:31:12,530 --> 00:31:16,250
One, two, three.

377
00:31:16,420 --> 00:31:18,010
Come on. Keep going. Don't stop.

378
00:31:18,010 --> 00:31:18,700
Four.

379
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:21,180
Remember to take your meds
after meals, alright?

380
00:31:26,460 --> 00:31:27,140
Nurse Liu

381
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,620
must be seeing someone.

382
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:29,730
And her new boyfriend

383
00:31:29,730 --> 00:31:30,980
is probably quite tall.

384
00:31:31,460 --> 00:31:32,900
She used to wear flats,

385
00:31:33,300 --> 00:31:34,730
now she wears height-boosting shoes.

386
00:31:35,250 --> 00:31:36,220
That boyfriend

387
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,660
is probably from Guangdong.

388
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:38,530
Nurse Liu

389
00:31:38,530 --> 00:31:40,180
is from the Northeast.

390
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:41,860
But just now, she said to me,

391
00:31:42,180 --> 00:31:44,860
"Yuci, remember to take your meds
after meals, alright?"

392
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,140
Good guess.

393
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:49,620
Try practicing on others.

394
00:31:51,940 --> 00:31:53,220
The one with glasses.

395
00:31:54,050 --> 00:31:55,250
Probably divorced.

396
00:31:55,940 --> 00:31:57,250
The one tossing his hair

397
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:59,290
might have childhood trauma.

398
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:01,380
You're very sharp.

399
00:32:02,730 --> 00:32:03,530
Remember.

400
00:32:05,250 --> 00:32:08,250
If you want to beat your rival,

401
00:32:08,250 --> 00:32:10,620
you have to know them first.

402
00:32:10,620 --> 00:32:13,090
One, two, three.

403
00:32:13,090 --> 00:32:13,810
Come on.

404
00:32:14,330 --> 00:32:15,050
Go!

405
00:32:15,050 --> 00:32:16,700
Without a strong body,

406
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:18,140
even the smartest mind

407
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:19,290
is pointless.

408
00:32:19,290 --> 00:32:20,460
Eat well, sleep well,

409
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:21,570
train hard.

410
00:32:21,570 --> 00:32:22,940
Outlive your rival.

411
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:24,420
That counts as winning too.

412
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:30,730
♪When the moon comes out, I ask myself♪

413
00:32:32,430 --> 00:32:38,850
♪Will forgiveness
help me sleep at night?♪

414
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:43,990
♪Two wrongs don't make a right♪

415
00:32:43,990 --> 00:32:45,760
♪That's what people say♪

416
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:48,440
♪But I have learned it the hard way♪

417
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:49,660
Master,

418
00:32:49,770 --> 00:32:51,220
remember to take your meds, alright?

419
00:32:51,730 --> 00:32:52,570
Alrighty.

420
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:57,290
Happy?

421
00:32:58,530 --> 00:32:59,330
Remember.

422
00:32:59,770 --> 00:33:00,730
Go over the materials.

423
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:03,330
Treatment is treatment.

424
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:05,900
But don't let them turn a genius
into a useless fool.

425
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:10,290
You're going into a battle
when you walk out of here.

426
00:33:11,090 --> 00:33:13,050
You won't just need
endurance and sharp eyes,

427
00:33:13,090 --> 00:33:14,460
you'll need to keep here running.

428
00:33:19,010 --> 00:33:20,090
At full speed.

429
00:33:22,490 --> 00:33:23,290
Alrighty.

430
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:27,900
Here,

431
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:28,620
you get to stand

432
00:33:28,620 --> 00:33:30,010
from a different angle

433
00:33:30,570 --> 00:33:31,460
and watch everything

434
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,810
that's happening out there.

435
00:33:34,050 --> 00:33:36,250
Then you can piece it together

436
00:33:36,250 --> 00:33:37,720
(Jiang Dongchao)
into a clear path forward.

437
00:33:37,770 --> 00:33:38,700
Everything in the past

438
00:33:38,700 --> 00:33:40,380
becomes crystal clear.

439
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:44,090
And the future is in your hands.

440
00:33:44,090 --> 00:33:45,460
(Sands Casino)

441
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:00,060
(Past)

442
00:34:01,420 --> 00:34:04,900
(Future)

443
00:34:13,260 --> 00:34:14,220
(Past: Chuxia)

444
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:19,380
(Future: Lysen)

445
00:34:23,740 --> 00:34:24,860
How can you be sure

446
00:34:25,340 --> 00:34:27,380
that all this will happen?

447
00:34:31,210 --> 00:34:33,010
When Li Qiang was out there gambling,

448
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:34,940
Li Mingxuan was with him.

449
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:38,420
Their greed will make sure

450
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,420
all of this happens.

451
00:34:41,090 --> 00:34:42,490
Once a dam starts leaking,

452
00:34:42,900 --> 00:34:44,010
there's no stopping it.

453
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:45,460
The flood will come fast

454
00:34:46,260 --> 00:34:47,420
and swallow everything.

455
00:34:49,490 --> 00:34:51,610
And what Bai Liangliang wants most

456
00:34:51,610 --> 00:34:53,340
is that position in Lysen.

457
00:34:54,010 --> 00:34:55,090
So my first move

458
00:34:55,090 --> 00:34:55,900
after entering Lysen

459
00:34:56,530 --> 00:34:57,980
was to take her spot.

460
00:35:02,260 --> 00:35:03,420
You know her.

461
00:35:03,940 --> 00:35:05,570
She won't just sit back and wait.

462
00:35:06,300 --> 00:35:08,050
So I have to find her weak spot.

463
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:11,500
(For Sale.
Quality Property. Serious Offer)

464
00:35:11,530 --> 00:35:14,300
I saw this on Bai Liangliang's phone.

465
00:35:15,860 --> 00:35:16,820
I memorized the number

466
00:35:16,820 --> 00:35:18,490
from the photo.

467
00:35:19,050 --> 00:35:20,650
Later, when I called it,

468
00:35:21,050 --> 00:35:23,090
I found out she had been
to that place many times.

469
00:35:24,010 --> 00:35:25,530
I have a feeling

470
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:27,170
that there's more to this place.

471
00:35:27,490 --> 00:35:29,170
There's probably a story behind it.

472
00:35:30,170 --> 00:35:31,570
And that story

473
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:34,420
might just be her weakness.

474
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:45,860
(For Sale.
Quality Property. Series Offer)

475
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:50,340
In that case, I'll use my connections

476
00:35:50,490 --> 00:35:52,090
to dig into this secret.

477
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:11,780
As you found out

478
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,380
from that loan company,

479
00:36:13,610 --> 00:36:14,940
the snowball keeps growing.

480
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,940
This is what Li Mingxuan owes now.

481
00:36:19,010 --> 00:36:20,780
13.05 million.

482
00:36:22,490 --> 00:36:23,690
You can use this

483
00:36:24,300 --> 00:36:25,420
to show a little sincerity.

484
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,010
Add a little sincerity,

485
00:36:35,570 --> 00:36:37,260
and win Jiang Dongchao's trust.

486
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:44,900
Li Qiang used five times leverage

487
00:36:45,780 --> 00:36:47,090
in the stock market,

488
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:49,340
trying to win back his losses
and cover the hole

489
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,300
from his gambling debts.

490
00:36:51,010 --> 00:36:51,820
Yet....

491
00:36:53,490 --> 00:36:54,980
You've got

492
00:36:54,980 --> 00:36:56,900
all their secrets now.

493
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:03,960
It's time to leave the hospital.

494
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:09,090
Right.

495
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:14,530
Time to wake up.

496
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:37,620
(Name: Rao Yuci,
Emergency Contact: Bai Liangliang)

497
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:41,780
(Initial Diagnosis, Admission Record,
Treatment Plan)

498
00:37:49,530 --> 00:37:50,340
Grandmother.

499
00:38:05,020 --> 00:38:08,700
=Episode 17=
(Secret Paradise)

500
00:38:09,181 --> 00:38:11,621
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

501
00:38:11,621 --> 00:38:17,821
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

502
00:38:18,581 --> 00:38:21,781
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

503
00:38:21,781 --> 00:38:26,301
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

504
00:38:26,301 --> 00:38:33,821
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

505
00:38:33,821 --> 00:38:37,741
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

506
00:38:37,741 --> 00:38:41,781
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

507
00:38:41,781 --> 00:38:45,301
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

508
00:38:45,301 --> 00:38:49,261
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

509
00:38:49,261 --> 00:38:53,421
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

510
00:38:53,421 --> 00:38:57,621
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

511
00:38:57,621 --> 00:39:01,421
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

512
00:39:01,421 --> 00:39:05,501
♪Keep walking through the light♪

513
00:39:05,501 --> 00:39:09,701
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

514
00:39:09,701 --> 00:39:16,021
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

515
00:39:33,141 --> 00:39:39,781
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

516
00:39:39,781 --> 00:39:43,621
♪An apology that came too late♪

517
00:39:43,621 --> 00:39:48,261
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

518
00:39:48,341 --> 00:39:55,741
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

519
00:39:55,741 --> 00:39:59,821
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

520
00:39:59,821 --> 00:40:03,901
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

521
00:40:03,901 --> 00:40:07,901
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

522
00:40:07,901 --> 00:40:11,661
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

523
00:40:11,661 --> 00:40:15,861
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

524
00:40:15,861 --> 00:40:20,021
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

525
00:40:20,021 --> 00:40:23,741
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

526
00:40:23,741 --> 00:40:27,781
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

527
00:40:27,781 --> 00:40:31,821
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

528
00:40:31,821 --> 00:40:38,021
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
